# CI/CD Pipeline with Docker and GitHub Actions

![CI/CD Pipeline](https://github.com/Shalini1920/cicd-docker-project/actions/workflows/pipeline.yml/badge.svg)

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates a **complete CI/CD pipeline** using:

- Docker
- GitHub Actions
- Docker Hub
- Automated Testing

Whenever code is pushed to the repository, the pipeline automatically:

1. Runs tests
2. Builds a Docker image
3. Pushes the image to Docker Hub

